    Fitting a CSDM model

    Fitting_a_CSDM_model.Rmd
    library(csdm)
    1. Let’s use the data provided in the package and taken from Delury’s population estimator data.
    delury <- csdm::delury_lobster
    1. Let’s run the model.
    delury_model <- csdm(catch = cpue,
                     effort = traps,
                     biomass = ~1,
                     q = ~1,
                     s = ~1,
                     data = delury,
                     prior = list(B0_logmean_prior_sd = log(1000),
                                  B0_group_prior_logsd = log(100)),
                     upper =  c(B0 = 1e10, q = 1e-3, s = 100),
                     chains = 4,
                     iter = 1000)
